Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At last, the KC Grand Prix has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter who my opponent is, it's decided I'll be the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the first round, my opponent is... Mask the Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what type of deck he's using,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm gonna beat him real quick and strip him of that mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy's using some really ridiculous strategies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that temple about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Illusionary Ancient Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Goblin Attack Force in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Ancient Giant with Goblin Attack Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open! The Permanent Trap, Ordeal of a Traveler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It activates when the opponent's Monster attacks me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It allows me to force the opponent to guess a card I hold in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it wrong, the attacking Monster must return to its owner's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have this one card! So guess it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's really thinking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because old man Sugoroku beat him at dice a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic? A Trap? A Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Like {\i1}hell{\i0} I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's a Magic! I've determined it's a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Looks like the luck you've depended on has run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not {\i1}luck{\i0}! {\i1}Ability{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ability..? Does he even know what he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good... Now Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} has no Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sugoroku-{\i1}san{\i0} attacks him directly next turn, then it's decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card! Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go now, Jounouchi! I Direct Attack the player with Ancient Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ancient Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Smash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open! Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me! I'm not just some Duelist relying on luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you try using your {\i1}head{\i0} a little the next time you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordeal of a Traveler is a Permanent Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning every time you attack, the quiz will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... W-Well, that's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just stay calm and think it through, I can guess your entire hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One of them has got to be the Killer Snake from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I know this, I can attack with my Monsters next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Continuous Magic Card from my hand, Ancient Book!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I just have that one Killer Snake to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Effect of Ancient Book allows me to switch a card in my hand with the card atop my Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch the Ancient Giant Tokens to Defense Mode and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the event the Ancient Giant Tokens don't attack the opponent's Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the player receives 500 points of damage to their Life for each.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's slashing his own Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why Defense Mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I take a gamble and attack again with Goblin Attack Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I guess it wrong this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll only have three Monsters, the Scapegoat Tokens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he draws another Monster next turn, I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But won't his card be Killer Snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Goblin Attack Force in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya damned coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's being completely dragged along by Old Man Sugoroku's pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but feel a bit bad for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time of death: 53 minutes after the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner! Leon Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...! Finally, we made it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dream! It's not an illusion! It's the real Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we got this far, we're gonna join that tournament, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We'll defeat Yugi and Jounouchi this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tossed aside our pride an' shamed ourselves long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got nothin' left ta' fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to keep Ancient Book on the field, I must discard one card to the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in turn, Killer Snake's Special Effect is activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is in the Graveyard during my Standby Phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can return it to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer Snake, come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fooling around with me or what, ya jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm long done fooling around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you've been busy ranting and raving,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been treasure hunting at my leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Treasure hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! The Legendary Dragon sleeping within Metropolis of Ancient Times - Ancient City!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the identity of my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Forbidden Door within Ancient City is opened, the Legendary Dragon will be revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have collected all the keys to the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I see...! So that's what he meant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch the Ancient Giant Tokens from Defense to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Switching the Battle Position of the Giant Stone Tokens must be a part of the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will then activate my Continuous Magic, Ancient Key!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack! Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By switching the Ancient Giant Tokens from a defensive stance to an offensive stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and offering up the Ancient Key as a holy tribute,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invoke the Ancient Door from my deck, hand or Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Effect of the Field Magic, Metropolis of Ancient Times - Ancient City activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ancient Door, Ancient Giant and Ancient Book are all gathered together on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sacrifice the three cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in turn reviving The Golden Dragon - Ancient Dragon from its age-old slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's Grandpa Sugoroku's treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Jounouchi? Surprised, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sugoroku really was playing for the Ancient Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient Dragon requires Ancient Door, Ancient Key...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ancient Book, Ancient Giant, and two Ancient Giant Tokens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't Summon it without these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you have to gather a hoard of mythical cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, like Sugoroku, I too have been searching all over for these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was never able to get the remaining card, Ancient Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, Sugoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello? It's me, Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get too shocked now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally found that card, the Ancient Door card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say {\i0}what{\i1} now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I have all the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sugoroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wanna see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-Well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, that's why I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To see everyone's surprised faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, that's just the kind of person Sugoroku is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good Duelist, but he loves the cards above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to fighting, he loves the cards more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when he got the card, he wanted to show it to all of us as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the greatest stage possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandfather's just like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if he's like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Monsters was originally created to allow people of all ages regain their lost childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugoroku truly enjoys this game for all it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoys? I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, how do you like my treasure?\NAmazing, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one little dragon. Don't let your ego go to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't brag about a deck like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... You've grown up to be a very boring man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll let you see firsthand just how great my treasure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Ancient Dragon to attack Goblin Attack Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go now, Ancient Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Bomb!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Sheep Tokens were destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient Dragon's Special Effect has activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I use this card to destroy the opponent's Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy all the Defense Mode Monsters on the opponent's field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't joke around...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I be defeated by this masked bastard here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna fight with Yugi again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to enjoy the Duel, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making this Duel too much about yourself! You have to enjoy it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... That ain't like you, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you win or lose this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Honda! Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Everyone... You are such nice people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just enjoy it, huh? Guess they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just cope with this Duel and let the match finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N You have to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, am enjoying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask the Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll go now, Masked Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Roll of Fate, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets the player draw the same number of cards as he rolls from his deck
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and remove the same amount of cards from his deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll use a Permanent Trap of my own! Legendary Gambler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My roll is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Bastard's is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booyah! I'll now activate Roll of Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Landstar Forces, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me Special Summon all Monsters with the name "Landstar"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level Three or lower from my hand in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Rifleman of Landstar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight of Landstar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Freedom Fighter of Landstar in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I sacrifice all three Landstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can Special Summon Gilford the Lightning in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate his Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you sacrifice three Monsters in order to Sacrifice Summon this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy every Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ancient Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet... Masked Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Gilford the Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll have to guess what this card is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, but I read through this already! That card is a Monster Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that really annoying snake bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilford the Lightning, Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Crush Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of the Field Magic, Ancient City!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this card is on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of the turn Ancient Dragon is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can be Special Summoned from the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon protected by the divine temple is impossible to destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's interesting...! This is what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Gilford the Lightning with Ancient Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both have 2800 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, they'll both be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Bomb!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilford the Lightning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's great about Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Pot of Greed from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw two cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurricane...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a Magic Card that returns all Magic and Trap Cards to the players' hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it... If I use this to return Ancient City to his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Premature Burial...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait... If I use this with Hurricane, my cards will also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! This ain't like you! Don't think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wing the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mask the Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering card after card while hiding your motives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of strategy after strategy, combo after combo like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really enjoying this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like this as well back when I first learned to Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started to forget this sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic Card, Premature Burial, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After paying 800 Life Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a Monster Card from my Graveyard and resurrect it in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive, Goblin Attack Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the Magic Card, Hurricane, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Hurricane's Special Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of our Magic and Trap Cards on the field will be returned to our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...! My temple...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Without the temple, Ancient Dragon can't revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my only aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will once again activate Premature Burial from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Gilford the Lightning from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Ancient Dragon with Gilford the Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Crush Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Goblin Attack Force, Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won by... using his {\i1}head{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Bastard, that was an interesting Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Sugoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, everyone?! It's me, Sugoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, old man! you sure like to mess with people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, I came to see you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your mentor, I wanted to see how your Dueling has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then? How was my Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really seemed to enjoy the Duel! You pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's passed {\i1}what{\i0}, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that grandpa of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he even come here for? I can't figure him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, right Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to enjoy yourself more than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first match of the tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi won against Sugoroku-{\i1}san{\i0}, A.K.A "Mask the Rock" as he proved his growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jounouchi didn't know it was Sugoroku-{\i1}san{\i0} until the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next game is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca will show up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and cheer for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her opponent is... Vivian Wong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! That strange woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hot Battle! Rebecca vs Vivian"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
